ine Forever</a></strong><span class="post_attribute center"><span class="post_detail_date">November 30, 2023</span> by <a href="https://crimereads.com/author/rebeccagibb/">Rebecca Gibb</a></span></div></li><li><div class="post_circle_thumb"><a href="https://crimereads.com/beyond-treasure-island-a-brief-introduction-to-pirates-in-fiction/"><img class="lazy" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/plugins/lb-content-widgets/img/lazy-sq.png" data-src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2023/11/pirate-novels-feat-150x150.jpg" alt=""></a></div><div class="text-container"><strong class="title"><a href="https://crimereads.com/beyond-treasure-island-a-brief-introduction-to-pirates-in-fiction/">Beyond <em>Treasure Island</em>: A Brief Introduction to Pirates in Fiction</a></strong><span class="post_attribute center"><span class="post_detail_date">November 30, 2023</span> by <a href="https://crimereads.com/author/katherinehowe/">Katherine Howe</a></span></div></li><li><div class="post_circle_thumb"><a href="https://crimereads.com/parties-gone-wrong-a-beloved-trope-in-crime-fiction/"><img class="lazy" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/plugins/lb-content-widgets/img/lazy-sq.png" data-src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2023/11/AdobeStock_309794016-150x150.jpeg" alt=""></a></div><div class="text-container"><strong class="title"><a href="https://crimereads.com/parties-gone-wrong-a-beloved-trope-in-crime-fiction/">Parties Gone Wrong: A Beloved Trope in Crime Fiction</a></strong><span class="post_attribute center"><span class="post_detail_date">November 30, 2023</span> by <a href="https://crimereads.com/author/harriettyce/">Harriet Tyce</a></span></div></li></ul></li>
